sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant Orch as /create-feature
    participant Arch as Architect
    participant FS as File system
    participant TEA as TEA agent
    participant W0 as Wave 0+

    U->>Orch: /create-feature F13 ...
    Orch->>Arch: didio spawn-agent architect
    Arch->>FS: write F13-README.md + F13-TYY.md
    Arch-->>Orch: DIDIO_DONE
    Orch->>FS: read didio.config.json:tea.enabled
    alt tea.enabled=false OR DIDIO_SKIP_TEA=1
        Orch->>W0: skip TEA → start Wave 0
    else tea.enabled=true
        Note over Orch: (if F10 merged: /check-readiness first)
        Orch->>TEA: didio spawn-agent tea
        TEA->>FS: read F13-README.md + tasks
        TEA->>FS: write F13-test-plan.md
        TEA->>FS: edit each F13-TYY.md (add **Test plan:**)
        TEA-->>Orch: DIDIO_DONE
        Orch->>W0: start Wave 0
    end
